{"tid":2167197,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"控方揭與妻在華有樓 女居港任律師  港產雙面諜「潛逃風險高」","createTime":"2020-08-21T02:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T03:18:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f05352584b34d125ded9854b12c0d6a145b54ada","tid":2167197,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:49:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/VR3HIEG2XRHIFIUPKCVTZTM6JE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FVR3HIEG2XRHIFIUPKCVTZTM6JE%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu1xDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=0f438089\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FVR3HIEG2XRHIFIUPKCVTZTM6JE%2F&h=b7035a1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/VR3HIEG2XRHIFIUPKCVTZTM6JE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n控方揭與妻在華有樓 女居港任律師 <br />\n港產雙面諜「潛逃風險高」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uJUB0xrdM2jE4-t3YCHCoFeM8Cs=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O7KZYUBUQVGIBGJE5IEUQ32B54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuJUB0xrdM2jE4-t3YCHCoFeM8Cs%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO7KZYUBUQVGIBGJE5IEUQ32B54.jpg&h=d9bdac79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港產雙面諜馬玉正（音譯）因向中國國安部門非法提供情報被美國當局起訴。<br />\n<br />\n【焦點追擊】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】先後任職美國中情局（CIA）及聯邦調查局（FBI）的港產雙面諜Alexander Yuk Ching Ma（音譯：馬玉正），因向中國國安部門非法提供情報被美國當局起訴，控方前日向法庭提交反對保釋的理據，透露馬有兩段婚姻，前妻的家庭至今仍在香港居住，其中一名女兒在港任職律師。控方指馬手握美國情報，面對最高刑罰是死刑的控罪，他很有可能以情報換取包括中國在內的外國情報機關協助逃亡，潛逃風險極高；保釋聆訊於美國時間昨日進行。<br />\n<br />\n控方在書面陳述指出，馬玉正被指控的是有系統的間諜罪行，屬非常嚴重控罪，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。安的卧底探員直認曾經向中國提供情報，更稱「我已經把所有資料都給了你們（中國國安）（I already gave you guys everything）」。<br />\n<br />\n控方又指，馬並非一般的疑犯，而是接受過情報訓練的人員，掌握秘密通訊及隱藏行蹤的技能，有能力輕易避過任何保釋。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控方反對保釋<br />\n<br />\n馬在香港曾有銀行戶口，並曾要求中國國安部門將錢存入該戶口。控方認為馬與中國有密切聯繫，一旦潛逃可以和妻子輕易在中國展開新生活，大大增加他潛逃的誘因，反對保釋。<br />\n<br />\n控方並指出，截至上周，馬玉正在家中仍管有中情局的文件，又向卧底探。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n67歲的馬玉正上周五被捕，他先後在80年代及00年代任職CIA及FBI，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"d649275326e0a904b2d2e9560eb4504f7be90b88","tid":2167197,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:52:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>先後任職美國中情局（CIA）及聯邦調查局（FBI）的港產雙面諜Alexander Yuk Ching Ma（音譯：馬玉正），因向中國國安部門非法提供情報被美國當局起訴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大中華發花癲之極致<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f45fcffb2ca225f79739baa571e83719c00ca26e","tid":2167197,"uid":26001,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:54:23.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死間諜，人類恥辱"},{"pid":"99a50521889b65da6a853c464c511047170b65e4","tid":2167197,"uid":346701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:58:46.000Z","msg":"呢D應該送去坐電椅"},{"pid":"8aa1fa110712c79a89c9ede5b1b21f4ff4b49d51","tid":2167197,"uid":124439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:00:46.000Z","msg":"收幾多錢都無用 肯定俾美國佬充公，最後都係一場空"},{"pid":"8c7267e26aabbf390a23105b02c9b8b5633918b2","tid":2167197,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:02:56.000Z","msg":"同之前另一單差唔多<br />\n<br />\n李振成間諜案<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9D%8E%E6%8C%AF%E6%88%90%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%258C%25AF%25E6%2588%2590%25E9%2596%2593%25E8%25AB%259C%25E6%25A1%2588&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu1xDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=13cdd2b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9D%8E%E6%8C%AF%E6%88%90%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E6%A1%88</a>"},{"pid":"201920fb27dff3692156bc708e5831bf5a84cc87","tid":2167197,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:13:22.000Z","msg":"趙家狗以為自己愛國<br />\n傻撚左"},{"pid":